'''贾斯旺·萨达陵墓'''（Jaswant Thada）是一座白色的大理石陵墓建筑，位于印度[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉贾斯坦邦]][[焦特布尔|焦特布尔]]。它是由焦特布尔的萨达·辛格王公于1899年修建，以纪念他的父亲贾斯旺.辛格二世<ref>{{cite book|last=Jain|first=Ajay|title=Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=tG9gAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT11|year=2013|publisher=Kunzum|page=11}}</ref> 。

贾斯旺·萨达陵墓内展示陈列着历代焦特布尔王公的肖像，<ref>{{cite book|title=The Indian Encyclopaedia: Indo-Pak War-Kamla Karri|author=Subodh Kapoor|year=2002|page=3755|quote= Jasvvant Thada, Close to the fort complex lies this white marble cenotaph, built in 1899, in commemoration of Maharaja Jaswant Singh II. Rare portraits of Jodhpur's rulers are also to be seen at Jaswant Thada.}}</ref>还有格子窗、花园及小湖泊。周围还有不少王公亲属的墓地。

